Invocation Name: popular repos
des:
Ask Alexa which new repositories have gotten a lot of stars! Ask Alexa to recommend a new repository to check out or a new commit to look at. You can hear about contributions to the open-source community as they happen!

Note: This skill is not affiliated with Github.com. It only uses the official API.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
